Rofi Beats - Windows
======================

This repository is a Windows reimplementation inspired by:
  Carbon-Bl4ck/Rofi-Beats
  https://github.com/Carbon-Bl4ck/Rofi-Beats

The current codebase was rewritten for Windows using PowerShell and WinForms,
rather than maintained as a line-by-line shell-script port.

Attribution is kept because the project name, initial direction, and a small
portion of the early station selection were inspired by the original project.

This repository keeps GPL-3.0 licensing to stay conservative about lineage and
reuse.

Unless otherwise noted, the current Windows implementation is authored by
repository contributors.
